rows.label: qst103404_msg0002
rows.name:
But are you sure you have time
to be wasting around here?

rows.label: qst103404_msg0003
rows.name:
What about the fellow who sent you
here, hmm? Do you think he's all right?

rows.label: qst103404_msg0004
rows.name:
Ahahah...
Got your attention now, have I?

rows.label: qst103404_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, if you'd like to go and check
up on him, don't let us stop you.
We of Brionac will be happy to wait.

rows.label: qst103404_msg0006
rows.name:
Hee hee hee...
Run along now, my dears!
